overnment to be able to have access, even with a search  warrant, to my keys... and I don't want those keys to be only 80 bits long  to begin with!  Hallelujah! :-) -- Rick M. Tait                                Bell Northern Research Europe Tel: +44-81-945-3352, Fax: +44-81-945-3352     Network Management Systems <PGP 2.2 public key available on request       New Southgate, London. UK email: ricktait@bnr.co.uk  || rt@cix.compulink.co.uk  ||  ricktait@bnr.ca"
